4. MFE Tracking Guide
4.1 Key Definitions
MFE (Maximum Favorable Excursion): Highest unrealized profit a trade reaches before exit.
MFEâ€‘Error: MFE minus actual profit captured. Express in R:
[(MFE â€“ Netâ€¯P/L) Ã· Stopâ€¯$].
